OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'will not walk away'
OL,4,Cafter Andy Burnham vows leadership
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer "will
OL,8,Fnot walk away" after Andy Burnham said
OL,9,Fhe will challenge him for the Labour
OL,10,Fleadership if he wins the Makerfield
OL,11,Fby-election.
OL,13,FDowning Street said the process for
OL,14,Fchallenging the Labour leader "has not
OL,15,Fbeen triggered", and that the country
OL,16,Fexpects ministers to "focus on
OL,17,Fgoverning".
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@NO]vD@_OUwD@OO]xD@VOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780625006
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'will not walk away'
OL,4,Cafter Andy Burnham vows leadership
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FThe Greater Manchester Mayor ` widely
OL,8,Fviewed as Sir Keir's main rival ` has
OL,9,Fpreviously promised a vote for him in
OL,10,FMakerfield would be a vote to "change
OL,11,FLabour" but had not explicitly said he
OL,12,Fwould launch a bid until pressed on
OL,13,Fthe BBC's Question Time by-election
OL,14,Fspecial.
OL,16,FAppearing on the programme on
OL,17,FThursday, Mr Burnham said a
OL,18,F"fundamental change" is needed in
OL,19,FWestminster to restore the public's
OL,20,Ftrust in politicians.
OL,26,@rD@_OUsD@GO]zD@AOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780625006
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'will not walk away'
OL,4,Cafter Andy Burnham vows leadership
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FAsked about his intentions if he wins
OL,8,Fthe seat, he said: "I'm not somebody
OL,9,Fwho gets ahead of myself. I can't do
OL,10,Fanything unless I'm lucky enough to
OL,11,Fget the support of people here," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"But if I get your support, I would
OL,15,Fseek to represent you at the highest
OL,16,Fpossible level and give this
OL,17,Fconstituency maximum power and
OL,18,Finfluence.
OL,26,@pD@TOUsD@`O]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780625006
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'will not walk away'
OL,4,Cafter Andy Burnham vows leadership
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"I think Wes Streeting seems to have
OL,8,Flaunched a leadership contest, so if
OL,9,Fthat is running, I would seek to join
OL,10,Fit. But I'd have to persuade members
OL,11,Fof the Parliamentary Labour Party to
OL,12,Fdo the same.
OL,14,F"So that's the only question... I've
OL,15,Fsaid to my team, let's have a proper
OL,16,Flook at this and let's develop a
OL,17,Fpolicy."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780625006
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'will not walk away'
OL,4,Cafter Andy Burnham vows leadership
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FThe former cabinet minister added:
OL,8,F"It's the point scoring, isn't it? You
OL,9,Fknow, the kind of whole set-up of
OL,10,FWestminster, people go to point-
OL,11,Fscoring before they go to problem-
OL,12,Fsolving.
OL,14,F"It's party first rather than place
OL,15,Ffirst and people collaborating. And it
OL,16,Ftook me a long time to realise it, but
OL,17,FI did realise it and that's why I
OL,18,Fleft."
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780625006
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'will not walk away'
OL,4,Cafter Andy Burnham vows leadership
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FHitting back at Mr Burnham, a No 10
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "With Keir
OL,9,FStarmer's leadership, this Labour
OL,10,FGovernment is supporting people with
OL,11,Fthe cost of living, cutting NHS
OL,12,Fwaiting lists, restoring control of
OL,13,Four borders and lifting half a million
OL,14,Fchildren out of poverty.
OL,16,F"The country expects us to focus on
OL,17,Fgoverning and to deliver change for
OL,18,Fhard-working people, not get
OL,19,Fdistracted by Westminster debates.
OL,26,@pD@TOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780625006
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'will not walk away'
OL,4,Cafter Andy Burnham vows leadership
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"The Labour Party has a process for
OL,8,Fchallenging a leader and it has not
OL,9,Fbeen triggered.
OL,11,F"The Prime Minister will not walk away
OL,12,Ffrom the mandate he was given just two
OL,13,Fyears ago to build a stronger, fairer
OL,14,FBritain."
OL,16,FMr Burnham is one of 14 candidates
OL,17,Fstanding in the election, which was
OL,18,Ftriggered when Labour's Josh Simons
OL,19,Fstood down.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
