FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780625006
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'will not walk away'
OL,4,Cafter Andy Burnham vows leadership
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FThe vote is expected to be a race
OL,8,Fbetween Mr Burnham and Reform UK's
OL,9,Fcandidate Robert Kenyon, a plumber and
OL,10,Flocal councillor.
OL,12,FA by-election poll released on
OL,13,FThursday evening showed Mr Burnham
OL,14,Fwith 49% of the vote, ahead of Mr
OL,15,FKenyon on 39%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
