PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780625006
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'will not walk away'
OL,4,Cafter Andy Burnham vows leadership
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FThe Survation poll, which had a sample
OL,8,Fsize of 518, put Rebecca Shepherd of
OL,9,FRestore Britain on 8% and Sarah
OL,10,FWakefield of the Green Party on 2%,
OL,11,Fwith the Lib Dems and Conservatives on
OL,12,F1%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
